Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp

Class TagLibraryDescriptor

java.lang.Object
org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp.TagLibraryDescriptor
public class TagLibraryDescriptor extends Object
Represents a parsed Tag Library Descriptor (TLD) containing tag definitions and metadata for a JSP tag library.

This class holds all information extracted from a .tld file, including:

  • Library metadata (version, shortname, URI, description)
  • Tag definitions with their handler classes and attributes
  • Function definitions for EL functions
  • Validation and other configuration settings
Author:
Chris Burdess
